</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_142" id="71r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Wilh<ex>e</ex>l<ex>m</ex></expan> Mendell,
                            <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Tewfel und Paulus Vörchtel,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> und <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> frewnd, uns ist von den
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und den
                            <expan>ambtlewt<ex>en</ex></expan>, die geleyt gen
                                <expan>Frankenf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>innenhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und geleyten
                            <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n,</expan>
<add>und auch von andern lewten</add> eygentlich kunt getan, daz die
                        furlewt, die ewr und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt hab und gut
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> gen
                            <expan>Frank<ex>furt</ex></expan> gefüret <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan>
                        den meistenteil on geleyt gefaren <add>und auch etlich
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>kawffl<ex>ewt</ex></expan> on
                            geleit <expan>geritte<ex>n</ex></expan> sein</add> und niht geleyt
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> noch <add>geleytsgelt</add> geben
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, davon wir
                                <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan></add> kawfflewt leib und guts
                                <expan>gross<ex>er</ex></expan> scheden
                            <expan>besorge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>und ein gross <expan>missfalle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>dara<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n,</ex></expan></add> wan uns die
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und auch ambtlewt
                            <expan>embotte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> ob also schad beschehe, daz sie
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> niht <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gepund<ex>en</ex></expan> sein. <add>So
                                <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> auch wir
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>ungehorsame<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>darinne</expan> niht <expan>hilffl<ex>ich</ex></expan> noch
                                    <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> sein</add>.
                                <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ist <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und <expan>heiss<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch,
                        daz ir all <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und kawfflewt
                            <expan>besend<ex>en</ex></expan>, <add>sie den brief hören lassen</add>
                        und in von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>untersag<ex>en</ex></expan> süllet, daz sie ir leib und gut fürbas
                        bas bewarn und on geleyt niht reiten, faren noch geen.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan>
<expan>sec<ex>re</ex>to.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
